{
  "stem": "5496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And again, just how I got there, I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I find myself back in Czechoslovakia, and I heard rumors that my mother is there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, they mixed her up with my aunt, because my aunt's husband was also a pharmacist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they said, the pharmacist's wife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And to my great delight, then, I found my aunt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She was waiting, yes, she was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But she was the only one who has returned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she's the one, then, who took care of me, literally, like an infant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My aunt was actually two years younger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the German family, up until the time when the Russian approached and they had to flee, themselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she went, right away, to the Russians, who brought her, then, within borders of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she doesn't know what happened to the family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To this day, she is not sure whether they know that she was-- she has a feeling-- he was a school director, very lovely, gentle people, with a daughter.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she always has a feeling that they knew who she was, but they pretended not to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while they had a lot of hardship, themselves-- by then, there was hardly any food and ration-- they shared with her, everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she managed to stay with them, as I said, until the Russians were right at the door, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't ask her, because it was just happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just knew that they, for some reason, we were not wanted, hated, and they wanted to annihilate us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I didn't ask her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wasn't a [INAUDIBLE] child that would ask mommy why.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just knew that it's because I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was fantastic, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
